{"tid":2276523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家唔好睇繼園臺七號","createTime":"2020-11-08T01:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T14:18:08.000Z","uid":137704,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03f8f09923847258af191cfb18f6b1e02fe23e56","tid":2276523,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64d73dT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64d73dT.png&h=c5d5293a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E7%B9%BC%E5%9C%92%E8%87%BA%E4%B8%83%E8%99%9F-%E6%A5%8A%E5%87%A1-%E7%B5%A6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E6%9B%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2583%25E8%2599%259F-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%2587%25A1-%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2yKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=ac41bd90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2583%25E8%2599%259F-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%2587%25A1-%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&h=7e7b89ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E7%B9%BC%E5%9C%92%E8%87%BA%E4%B8%83%E8%99%9F-%E6%A5%8A%E5%87%A1-%E7%B5%A6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E6%9B%B8/</a><br />\n繼園臺七號依家係戲院上映緊，連立場新聞都有出文講動畫入面香港情懷。<br />\n<br />\n但係，睇番個導演楊凡講過啲咩就知唔洗去睇。<br />\n&quot;他上台領獎時亦向香港致意：「我好興奮，真的好興奮。因為我拍了40年電影，大家總是抱怨我的電影沒有劇情，今日，現在我卻拿了最佳劇本獎！我也想感謝香港，給我所有自由讓我創作。我因為戒嚴從台灣來到香港，我在海邊就聞到自由，在街道就聞到自由。<span class=\"red\">52年後，不知從何來的另一股奇怪力量以自由、人權及民主之名，令香港反轉。讓我們無法自由搭乘大眾交通工具外出。現時正如打開了潘朵拉盒子，好多邪惡的人從盒子內走出來互鬥。但我覺得潘朵拉盒子總會有希望，我希望香港可以回復正常，令我們可以再次感受自由。多謝大家 ！</span>」楊凡亦在社交網轉載得獎感言，立即惹來網民爭論。&quot;"},{"pid":"e90a437acee20e68f75767be52ea5b87375fa578","tid":2276523,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c5e7adb341365115aa6f34f2e6e67c77b835b54f","tid":2276523,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"14061222351bca884e354ef30b6d32fd0d83455a","tid":2276523,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"本身有啲想睇，好彩search一search"}]}